Module com.example.projectthree
Package com.example.Projv3

Class Member

java.lang.Object
com.example.Projv3.Member
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Member>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Family
public class Member extends Object implements Comparable<Member>
This is the member class which has the different attributes when it is passed from add. The attributes include, first name, last name, date of birth, expiration of memebership, and location of membership. This class also has an equals method as a way of comparing two members together. It includes different ways of also setting a member object.
Author:
Abhijeet Singh, Khizar Saud
